  "text": "Slices were preincubated in gassed ACSF for 10 min at 35°C. They were then transferred to a gassed Mg 2+ -free ACSF chamber with a mix of 100 µM picrotoxin, 50 µM forskolin and 0.1 µM rolipram, and incubated for 8 min. Control conditions were performed in ACSF containing normal levels of Mg 2+ with DMSO as vehicle [CITATION_1] .",
